# Tailwind conventions

- Prefer Tailwind utilities over custom CSS.
- Use `cn()` from `src/lib/cn.ts` when composing classnames.
- Extract repeated classname patterns into components (or variants) instead of copy/paste.
- Light mode only for now (no dark-mode toggle or `dark:` styling unless explicitly requested).

